Private Sub Display_AnimationStart()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler
Dim INSTRUMENTO As String
INSTRUMENTO = Text1.Caption PONTEIRO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 4, 1)
If PONTEIRO = "-" Then INSTR_TIPO = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 1) INSTR_NUMERO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 5) Else INSTR_TIPO = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 2) INSTR_NUMERO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 6) End If
AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = " EventSource LIKE '" & INSTR_TIPO & "' And EventSource LIKE '" & INSTR_NUMERO & "'"
Exit Sub ErrHandler:
End Sub
